Give A Shit. 
Ask For Help. 
Get Involved. 
Let’s Learn Together how to Fight and Finish the Battle of Systemic Racism. 
100% of your donation benefits these initiatives:

Black Lives Matter - @osopepatrisse 
Florida Rights Restoration Coalition 
Know Your Rights Camp 
Center for Policing Equity
Color of Change 
Bail Project 
To donate or RSVP for the event 
click the link in my bio. 
Thank You

Ps... we’re totally reading a scene from TATB3

@favorednations 
@favorednations

node.text: I’ve been looking for a way to actually connect with you and finally found it. I’ll let you know when I’m in your city, when I get a new role, when a book I’m excited about comes out, when I can’t sleep and want to know who else is thinking about some crazy shit, When I learn something new, whenever. I’ll text you first. So hit my line +(561)-220-0860

node.text:
Enter to win a chance to join me at the premiere of “To All The Boys: PS I Still Love You” on Feb. 3 in Los Angeles!

Rules to enter:
Step 1: Follow @favorednations
Step 2: Enter your email at FavoredNations.org (link in bio)
Step 3: Tag a friend below you’d invite
.
.
Entry ends 01.31 at 12PM PST. One winner will be chosen at random and contacted via DM on Friday, 01.31. Void where prohibited by law. This giveaway is in no way sponsored, administered, or associated with Instagram or Netflix. By entering, entrants confirm that they are 18+ years of age, United States residents, release Instagram of responsibility and liability, and agree to Instagram's terms of use.
